ivardefs.name: instruction
ivardefs.desc: Free text or additional instructions or information pertaining to the oral supplement.

ivardefs.name: productName
ivardefs.desc: The product or brand name of the nutritional supplement such as "Acme Protein Shake".

ivardefs.name: quantity
ivardefs.desc: The amount of the nutritional supplement to be given.

ivardefs.name: schedule_
ivardefs.desc: The time period and frequency at which the supplement(s) should be given.  The supplement should be given for the combination of all schedules if more than one schedule is present.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: The kind of nutritional supplement product required such as a high protein or pediatric clear liquid supplement.

properties.desc: Oral nutritional products given in order to add further nutritional value to the patient's diet.
